text:
Hey, it's okay.
...Is it about today's work?

Yes...
I feel like I didn't do very well...

Being in a new place, surrounded by new people,
it's natural to feel a bit lost.

If anything, I should've supported you more.
I owe you an apology...

T-That's not...
It's because I got nervous and stiffened up...

I'll do my best to make it easier for you to work, Mano.
...Let's take it slowly, getting used to things.
